## 📁 System Core Files
- [bert_predict.py](file:///c:/Users/98858/.gemini/antigravity/playground/golden-apollo/bert_predict.py): Uses the pre-trained RoBERTa pipeline.
- [app.py](file:///c:/Users/98858/.gemini/antigravity/playground/golden-apollo/app.py): Implements the 4-layer Hybrid Decision Flow.
- [predict.py](file:///c:/Users/98858/.gemini/antigravity/playground/golden-apollo/predict.py): Core SVM and Decision Engine integration.

