- [predict.py](file:///c:/Users/98858/.gemini/antigravity/playground/golden-apollo/predict.py) & [bert_predict.py](file:///c:/Users/98858/.gemini/antigravity/playground/golden-apollo/bert_predict.py): Refined to focus on probability generation and passing control to the engine.
